features: 【Brand Overview】Thermalright is a Taiwan brand with more than 20 years of development. It has a certain popularity in the domestic and foreign markets and has a pivotal influence in the player market. We have been focusing on the research and development of computer accessories. R & D product lines include: CPU air-cooled radiator, case fan, thermal silicone pad, thermal silicone grease, CPU fan controller, anti falling off mounting bracket, support mounting bracket and other commodities.

【Product specification】Thermalright AK120 SE; CPU Cooler dimensions: 120(L)x73(W)x148(H)mm/ (4.92x2.87x 5.83 inch); Product weight:0.8kg(1.76lb); heat sink material: aluminum, CPU cooler is equipped with metal fasteners of Intel & AMD platform to achieve better installation.

【PWM Fan】Model:TL-C12C; Standard size PWM fan:120x120x25mm (4.72x4.72x0.98 inches); fan speed (RPM):1550rpm±10%; power port: 4pin; Voltage:12V; Air flow:66.17CFM(MAX); Noise Level≤25.6dB(A), the fan pairs efficient cool with low-noise-level, providing you an environment with both efficient cool and true quietness.

【AGHP technique】5×6mm heat pipes apply AGHP III technique, Solve the Inverse gravity effect caused by vertical / horizontal orientation, cpu cooler TDP is 235W. Up to 20000 hours of industrial service life, S-FDB bearings ensure long service life of air-cooler radiators. UL class a safety insulation low-grade, industrial White PBT + PC material to create high-quality products for you. The height is 148mm, Suitable for medium-sized computer case.
【Compatibility】The CPU cooler Socket supports: Intel: LGA 1150/1151/1155/1156/1200/1700/17XX, AMD:AM4; For different CPU socket platforms, corresponding mounting plate or fastener parts are provided.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Perfect cooler, cheap, aesthetic, my CPU is under 65 degrees playing. Easy to install.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Powerful air cooler for bargain price
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful and powerful cpu air cooler. Installation is easy. The maximum temperature of my new AMD 5600X3D was 79 degrees C during Cinebench 2024 benchmark run with room temperature at 25 degrees C.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An absolute rare bargain
reviews.reviewText: Initial purchase review - will update with practical application review post installationThis is an incredible value for the cost, I really can not believe I bought this cooler for 17 bucks. 5 Direct contact copper heat pipes, on inspection the machine work looks and feels fine/smooth. Far better than I was expecting at this price point.If you wanted to make it even better you could give it a polish finish with a fine grit sand paper and polish wheel, but it looks good enough to slap on out of the box if you just need basic cooling and aren't looking to optimize every factor.The fit and finish on the metal components is extraordinarily impressive at this price point. I have Noctua, coolermaster, Intel, AMD, dell, HP 2u server and all sorts of Chinesium CPU coolers and it really is hard to believe they're able to produce this item at its cost, that or we've all been seriously overpaying for CPU coolers.The fan looks good and has a high quality feel to the plastic, it's dense and similar in material to other much more expensive PC fans that I own. The mounting components seem pretty average generic tower cooler stuff done in style of a Noctua mount with one screw per side in the middle of the cooler that screw into metal plates that screw into the backing.Will update post install/testing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The fan serves its purpose, cooling...but is also quiet and very cool to look at! Was easy yo set up, and it works just great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really like the design and the performance of this CPU cooler. The reason I give 4 stars is the fact that the tower is slightly offset. For the price it works very well tho. Tested with two CPUs (12100 and 12600). Both performing great around 60C (i3) and 67C (i5) in Cinebench.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install temps are great
reviews.reviewText: Not much to say really - easy to install, works great for cooling my 3700x, slim, great price, aesthetics are nice.Recommended for a slim, cheap, effective cooler.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Installed Flawlessly with Z690 Chipset MB LGA 1700
reviews.reviewText: The installation of this CPU cooler was straightforward on the LGA 1700 socket.Provides fantastic cooling to the i5-12600KF processor and the 5 copper contact bars are nice upgrade.With this CPU cooler the i5-12600KF runs in our tests around 50 C and under load about 70 C which is great for gaming and overclocking.Great value for the money as it is a higher quality cooler at lower end price!

reviews.reviewerName: Amazing for the price the bend is a lil weird but still feels good

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best budget cpu fan
reviews.reviewText: The 6 pack of the same fans are good and cheap a good budget friendly cooling system amazing brand

This photo is after 30 minutes of full load. Yesterday in 20 minutes I would hit 90c in the same amount of time. CHEAP QUIET AND WORTH ITS MONEY IN GOLD.I like to add anything negative I can (this is the best I got)The fan cable was about 1/2 inch shorter then I would have liked. reviews.reviewTitle: Excelente calidad! Sin duda la mejor opción para cambiar el de stock.
reviews.reviewText: Tenía temperatura de hasta 80° ahora 55°-60° en videojuegos y en uso normal unos 35°-40° se mantiene. Para el precio la verdad es fabuloso! Vendedor thermalight direct 2 recomendado! Llegó en tiempos y forma.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excelente disipador para procesadores de bajo TDP
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Es bastante fácil de instalar, se ve bien, y me redujo hasta en 10°C las temperaturas en idle y hasta 15° C en carga de juegos.Estaba indeciso entre este y el Peerless Assassin, pero iba a tapar mis dims de RGB y siendo realistas los 65w que usa mi 5700x no lo requerían.Mejor que el 212 en mi experiencia personal y mucho más barato en el momento que lo compré, además que en blanco quedó super bien para mi gabinete.

Product came intact, no issues, delivered earlier than scheduled. After installation, the product works fine, my i5-12400f became 20 degrees cooler compared to stock cooler. I was constantly hitting 80+ degrees with stock cooler and now it doesn't go beyond 60 degrees if installed properly. My house is not a cold place, it is warm and humid so I'm impressed with the coolers performance. Worth the buy 👍.
Sumamente económico y sumamente silencioso, trabaja enfriando un ryzen 7 5700x sin problema alguno
